query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) as total_properties,
  COUNT(DISTINCT pt.propertyId) as properties_with_tags,
  COUNT(pt.id) as total_tags
FROM properties p
LEFT JOIN propertyTags pt ON p.id = pt.propertyId
WHERE p.listName = 'Rolando' OR pt.tag = 'rolando_import';
